{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778377110268,"sessionID":"ses_1f07e2ebdffeInlu2gX9ePTiIa","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_RdRRHpyOUz2LeGFWhWzKzFjs","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/terms/GO_1990334.obo","offset":1,"limit":100},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/terms/GO_1990334.obo</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: [Term]\n2: id: GO:1990334\n3: name: Bfa1-Bub2 complex\n4: namespace: cellular_component\n5: def: \"A protein complex that acts as a two-component GTPase-activating protein for Tem1 GTPase, thus regulating a signal transduction cascade, called the mitotic exit network (MEN), which is required for mitotic exit and cytokinesis. Bub2/Bfa1 keeps Tem1 inactive until the spindle is properly oriented, thus inhibiting MEN activation.\" [GOC:bhm, PMID:16449187]\n6: is_a: GO:1902773 ! GTPase activator complex\n7: relationship: part_of GO:0005816 ! spindle pole body\n8: created_by: bhm\n9: creation_date: 2014-03-17T14:34:21Z\n10: \n\n(End of file - total 10 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"[Term]\nid: GO:1990334\nname: Bfa1-Bub2 complex\nnamespace: cellular_component\ndef: \"A protein complex that acts as a two-component GTPase-activating protein for Tem1 GTPase, thus regulating a signal transduction cascade, called the mitotic exit network (MEN), which is required for mitotic exit and cytokinesis. Bub2/Bfa1 keeps Tem1 inactive until the spindle is properly oriented, thus inhibiting MEN activation.\" [GOC:bhm, PMID:16449187]\nis_a: GO:1902773 ! GTPase activator complex\nrelationship: part_of GO:0005816 ! spindle pole body\ncreated_by: bhm\ncreation_date: 2014-03-17T14:34:21Z\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"terms/GO_1990334.obo","time":{"start":1778377110261,"end":1778377110267}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_010f892b88f50bec0169ffe195d04081a0a86cde09797c8dc9"}},"id":"prt_e0f89314e001QsYOakfsk5TIyQ","sessionID":"ses_1f07e2ebdffeInlu2gX9e